  "text": "where w 0 is the vertical nodal deformation vector of the pile; w 0 is the vector of the vertical free-field soil deformation induced by tunnelling; I 0 is the vertical soil flexibility matrix, which can be found in [CITATION_1] for a layered soil system; q 0 is Mathematical Problems in Engineering the vertical nodal soil resistance force vector of the pile; u 0 is the horizontal nodal displacement vector of the pile; u 0 is the vector of the horizontal free-field soil deformation induced by tunnelling; I 0 is the horizontal soil flexibility matrix, which can be found in [CITATION_2] for a layered soil system; and p 0 is the horizontal nodal soil resistance force vector of the pile.",
